"},{"pid":"4f0a5ab92e99f5e781cb1d1a8c06954c493ae91b","tid":155259,"uid":37623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"可能真係有內彎 我拉筋右腳會痛d 唔知關唔關事 令正返隻腳咁拉筋 會無咁痛 大家可唔可以教我邊到睇物理治療 會唔會好貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3967bc3a047156fe54402734d9a9bd32c3548866","tid":155259,"uid":37623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"我70kg 175高 半年重左10 kg  做gym有做腿部肌肉訓練 唔覺有幫助"},{"pid":"96aa49fab45f9d231c43dc67f17b793689b5ee5a","tid":155259,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"跑完用冰敷<br />\n試下食關節素"},{"pid":"f07c8d5eea29b6fe898f589628d2de4c39666b70","tid":155259,"uid":64457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"傷左要休息番幾個月好番先可以繼續跑"},{"pid":"ad1de90338504fecddec6fe57c892390414abc04","tid":155259,"uid":33256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>膝頭有事未必適合跑步 睇醫生<br />\n或者嘗試其他帶氧運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問邊度睇好點？ 如果去醫 會唔會好貴 因為仲讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港都有好多不同種類嘅物理治療 你要搵到啱你自己 同時您又相信個醫師先有用<br />\n建議您去游水&gt;跑步<br />\n不過有膝傷就要避免游蛙式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cddd4533767ce858120666cc1ae86dc11a91650","tid":155259,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"跑完之後要做cool down . 最好就係草地到行 , 慢跑"},{"pid":"0df295ca07bf7b458e5011add6b8d26472b7e2ba","tid":155259,"uid":7476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"wram up cool dowm 好重要，而家敷住冰先 每日三次 ，之後用roller 按摩下大臂 全方位 。 做四頭肌 exercise"}]}